[explanation]

User following functions to complete this test.

<pre class="code javascript" >
function download( callback ) { ... };
function save( file ) { ... };
</pre>

## Write a callback

* the callback should _accept_ an argument
* _call_ `save` with the argument, but only when it is **not null**
* finally, _call_ `download` with the `callback` as the argument

[zone name:script.js for:function_callbacks syntax:javascript]
download( /* callback */ )
[test source:test.js]
